WEBVTT

01:22.040 --> 01:23.320 line:80%
early in the morning.

01:23.500 --> 01:25.460 line:80%
The neighbors can all prove that!

01:25.480 --> 01:26.940 line:80%
Yes, we can prove that!

01:26.960 --> 01:28.500 line:80%
-We can testify for Changyu!
-Last night,

01:28.500 --> 01:30.420 line:80%
-Changyu was at home!
-Yes!

01:30.420 --> 01:31.140 line:80%
And we came here

01:31.140 --> 01:32.740 line:80%
-with her in the morning!
-County Magistrate!
